    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_3125_3",
    "text": "①六安爷用这句话来回应村人的劝阻，由此能感受到他温和而又固执的性格特征；",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.06049243844519435,
      0.2782222222222222,
      0.7279090113735783,
      0.3244444444444444
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_3125",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_3125_4",
    "text": "② 百亩园即将不复存在，六安爷的眼睛也快要失明，他要过在百亩园劳作的“瘾”，由此能体会 到他内心的隐痛。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.05699287589051369,
      0.33866666666666667,
      0.8468941382327209,
      0.4444444444444444
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_3125",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_3125_5",
    "text": "小说主旨层面：",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.06099237595300588,
      0.4613333333333333,
      0.1864766904136983,
      0.5031111111111111
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_3125",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_3125_6",
    "text": "①在大地上劳作是一种“瘾”，即劳动者的精神需要；",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.06099237595300588,
      0.5191111111111111,
      0.5064366954130733,
      0.5635555555555556
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_3125",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_3125_7",
    "text": "② 随着传统的农业生产、生活方式的结束，精神的意义只剩下“过瘾”，令人叹惋又发人深思 。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
